    <div><p>Publisher <a title="Companies > Sony Interactive Entertainment [5,049 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sony-group-corporation/sony-interactive-entertainment">Sony Interactive Entertainment</a> and developer <a title="Companies > Sucker Punch Productions [154 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/companies/sony-group-corporation/sony-interactive-entertainment/sucker-punch-productions">Sucker Punch Productions</a> have released a 10-minute video for <em><a title="Games > Ghost of Yotei [6 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/games/ghost-of-yotei">Ghost of Yotei</a></em> dubbed “Journey Through the Edge of Japan,” which showcases the landscapes of Ezo to an extended version of the original track “The North” composed by Toma Otowa. <span id="more-990415"></span></p><p><em>Ghost of Yotei</em> is due out for <a title="Platforms > PS5 [10,320 articles]" href="https://www.gematsu.com/platforms/playstation/ps5">PlayStation 5</a> on October 2.</p><p>Watch the video below.</p><h2><span>Journey Through the Edge of Japan</span></h2><p><iframe title="Ghost of Yōtei - Journey Through The Edge Of Japan Video | PS5 Games" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/kj6i1eCfIgA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></p></div>

        
    
